<figureCitation box="[527,613,1072,1098]" captionStart="FIGURES 94–97" captionStartId="134.[151,269,1253,1277]" captionTargetBox="[157,1431,195,1228]" captionTargetId="figure-55@134.[151,1436,194,1231]" captionTargetPageId="134" captionText="FIGURES 94–97. Known distribution of Uracanthus species: 94, U. bicoloratus, U. maculatus, U. perthensis, U. griseus, and U. glabrilineatus; 95, U. triangularis; 96, U. pallens; 97, U. regalis and U. dubius." pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Fig. 94</figureCitation>
